Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢 去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狹窄啊 四個人能一起擠進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要推我啦 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生都會操作呢 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 你在那種地方做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不用只站著看了 你也來一起拍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 和我們一起來拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快點過來吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來嘛 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 真琴在最中間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像能加上手寫的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能加上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 真琴發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微穩定下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想要的嗎 要不要我買肉包子來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真琴只要和我在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是如此就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我念書給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜歡的那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡著了哦 馬上就要給你念了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 故事開始 故事開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛總是突然降臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這孩子有什麼願望的話 請無論如何幫她實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 一定會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我們就可以在一起了 結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想結婚 結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和祐一結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去結婚吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真琴能起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們兩人要外出一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然蹺課不上學 真是不良學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 我會準備好美味的晚飯等著你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翹課嗎 我們倆還真是壞學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我什麼都做不了 但如果只是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也是她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算接下來先路過學校再到山丘去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎 我覺得這樣挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個山丘是這孩子誕生的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們在此分別
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託你傳個話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 是水瀨名雪前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 改天我們再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為她想和你玩一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 雖然現在是午休沒那麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩什麼呢 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 等你回來了再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 有好多事情都想和真琴說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 那麼待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也坐下來
