Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 差不多要開始了
