Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心嗎 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 真琴 輪到你了
