Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別睡呀 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 繼續玩鈴鐺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚…啊嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 這次輪到我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直這樣玩下去就好了 對吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 又輪到你了 聽見我說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮呤叮呤地搖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真琴 真…
