Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來吧 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 真琴在最中間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是春天來了 然後一直是春天就好了
